### Icon position

When using an icon in a button or list, you can set an icon’s position before or after the text. Use the parameter `iconPosition` and give it a value of either “before” or ”after”.

### Icon size

When using an icon in the panel component, you can change it’s size from the default (sized to regular text) to match the size of the text set by the [typography type scale](/foundations/typography/#type-scale). Use the parameter `iconSize` and give it a value of either: “s”, “m”, “l”, “xl”, “xxl” or “xxxl”.
{{
